    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The barrel of this long rifle is translucent in places, forming a swirled pattern along the metal, and its stock is formed of crimson wood. *Ghosthand's Comet* is a *+4 major striking beast-bane greater impactful advanced firearm* with a range increment of 300 feet. It deals 5d8 force damage and has the backstabber, concussive, kickback, and fatal d12 traits. As a star gun, *Ghosthand's Comet* runs on magic and doesn't use ammunition or black powder. The weapon is silent when fired.",
        "level": 23,
        "image": {
            "type": "image",
            "name": "Ghosthand's Comet",
            "image": "Ghosthands_Comet.webp"
        },
